# Ignored when building from this directory's context. Note: per
# docs/09-deployment-ops.md the canonical build is from the repo root with
# `-f apps/web/Dockerfile`, so the root context applies — but ship this
# alongside to keep per-app builds clean too.

# Dependencies and build artifacts
node_modules
**/node_modules
.next
**/.next
dist
**/dist
build
**/build
out
**/out
coverage
**/coverage

# VCS and editor
.git
.gitignore
.idea
.vscode
*.swp
*.swo

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Env files (never bake secrets into the image)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Logs and tmp
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
.dev
tmp

# Test artifacts
test-results
playwright-report
.nyc_output

# Docs and meta — not needed inside the image
README.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
SECURITY.md
CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
HISTORY.md
ROADMAP.md
LICENSE
adr
docs

# Other apps and tooling not needed for this image's build
apps/api
apps/worker
cli
plugins
themes
migrations
go.work
go.work.sum
**/*.go
